These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the fan of pop and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, mirinda, tea
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the owner of the ferret and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | mirinda | cola     | tea |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: funk, r&b, soul
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the fan of funk is the owner of the bird##1
2. the fan of soul is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b  | soul     | funk |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, dutch
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the brazilian is between the person eating pineapple and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian | dutch     |

