.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, weightlifting
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | swimming  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, social-worker
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the person driving the quad-bike and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer | fisherman |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person drinking fanta and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

